Version:        1.12
Release:        6%{?dist}
Summary:        DNSSEC modules for Perl
License:        MIT
URL:            https://metacpan.org/release/Net-DNS-SEC
Source0:        https://cpan.metacpan.org/authors/id/N/NL/NLNETLABS/Net-DNS-SEC-%{version}.tar.gz
